   <head>Jn Artem amandi <hi>Decastichon.</hi>
   </head>
   <l>EXimiè scripsit <hi>Cicero,</hi> benè pinxit <hi>Apelles,</hi>
   </l>
   <l>Inuidiae morsum sensit vterque tamen.</l>
   <l>Conscia mens recti cum te comitetur euntem,</l>
   <l>Sperne venenato quicquid ab ore fluit.</l>
   <l>Quòd liber est nitidus, miscetur &amp; vtile dulci,</l>
   <l>Dexter <hi>Apollo</hi> tibi; Fama perennis erit.</l>
   <l>Ergo macte animo, nec publica cōmoda tardes,</l>
   <l>Ingenij viuent sic monumenta tui.</l>
   <l>Candidus Interpres laudetur, &amp; optimus Au<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>thor,</l>
   <l>Viuat vterque diu, cedat vtrique decus.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>FRANCISCVS MERES.</signed>
   </closer>
